overview: The doctor will see you now – but don’t expect any of these horny medics to be satisfied with anything other than a thorough and very intimate examination! Indeed, there’s nothing glib or half-hearted for the patients here; as STAXUS favourites, Shane Hirch, Tom Nutt, Milan Sharp and the mega-hung Jace Reed show fresh-faces such as Chad Johnstone and Zach Hansen that a top-class medical check-up involves more than a simple “Cough & Drop”. More like open wide, fuck raw and hard, and dump copious amounts of pent-up twink-juice!
title: Raw Medics
